ecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1566880/extras/dcbe56b43de14ee71d7db6f9841c4777.mp4?t=1750782355\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Create a personalized avatar as your character.<br>You can also upload your avatar and other players can add it to their party.<br>Character costumes and weapons can also be customized without affecting their specs by using Visualize Attire.",
